Class TestNGEngineForGivenClientBasedModules

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atmecs.falcon.automation.util.main.AbstractTestNGEngine

        • com.atmecs.falcon.automation.util.main.TestNGEngineForGivenClientBasedModules

  • public class TestNGEngineForGivenClientBasedModules
extends TestNGEngineForDesiredSuites
    Purpose is to create suites with the combination of clients and modules provided at the run time. For example : -DClientName=c1,c2,c3 are the client name. -DModuleName=m1:m2,m2,m1:m2:m3 are the modules name. Here for client c1 it will run module m1 and m2, for client c2 it will run module m2 only.
